3eSave $270.00\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Roam 2 is their version of a portable, and like most Sonos speakers, they integrate seamlessly into the ecosystem to play multi-room media. It has a speakerphone feature, in-app EQ, wireless charging, is water resistant, and has Alexa and Sonos voice assistant, according to \u003ca href=\"https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/sonos-roam-2\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ePCMag\u0026#39;s review\u003c/a\u003e. At \u003cstrong\u003e$139\u003c/strong\u003e (originally $179), the \u003ca data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-template=\"Deals\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" data-ga-element=\"offer\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-event_label=\"Roam 2\" href=\"https://zdcs.link/aX2e8B?pageview_type=Standard\u0026amp;template=Deals\u0026amp;module=content_body\u0026amp;element=offer\u0026amp;item=text-link\u0026amp;element_label=Roam%202\u0026amp;short_url=aX2e8B\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ftech%2Fsonos-speaker-amazon-sale\u0026amp;event_label=Roam%202\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eRoam 2\u003c/a\u003e is the cheapest way to try a Sonos speaker.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-template=\"Deals\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" data-ga-element=\"offer\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-event_label=\"Sonos Era 100\" href=\"https://zdcs.link/aewYZl?pageview_type=Standard\u0026amp;template=Deals\u0026amp;module=content_body\u0026amp;element=offer\u0026amp;item=text-link\u0026amp;element_label=Sonos%20Era%20100\u0026amp;short_url=aewYZl\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ftech%2Fsonos-speaker-amazon-sale\u0026amp;event_label=Sonos%20Era%20100\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eSonos Era 100\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e is a smart speaker that can work as stereo with a pair or as rear speakers in a Sonos surround sound system. It is an updated version of the Sonos One smart speaker, offering better bass and other improvements. It has an \u0026#34;excellent\u0026#34; \u003ca href=\"https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/sonos-era-100\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ereview from PCMag\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e for its ability to play stereo with a single device (it has a dual tweeter setup), its balanced audio, and the well-developed companion app that allows you to adjust the EQ.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-template=\"Deals\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" data-ga-element=\"offer\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-event_label=\"Sonos Sub Mini\" href=\"https://zdcs.link/z3RW4m?pageview_type=Standard\u0026amp;template=Deals\u0026amp;module=content_body\u0026amp;element=offer\u0026amp;item=text-link\u0026amp;element_label=Sonos%20Sub%20Mini\u0026amp;short_url=z3RW4m\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ftech%2Fsonos-speaker-amazon-sale\u0026amp;event_label=Sonos%20Sub%20Mini\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eSonos Sub Mini\u003c/a\u003e is a smaller and more affordable version of the Sonos Sub, perfect for a small apartment or room where you want a soundbar and subwoofer combo. You can read the \u003ca href=\"https://www.cnet.com/tech/home-entertainment/sonos-sub-mini-review-solid-for-music-not-as-good-for-home-theater/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eCNET review here\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd if you\u0026#39;re looking for a top-notch soundbar, consider the \u003ca data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-template=\"Deals\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" data-ga-element=\"offer\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-event_label=\"Sonos Arc\" href=\"https://zdcs.link/zj4qxr?pageview_type=Standard\u0026amp;template=Deals\u0026amp;module=content_body\u0026amp;element=offer\u0026amp;item=text-link\u0026amp;element_label=Sonos%20Arc\u0026amp;short_url=zj4qxr\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ftech%2Fsonos-speaker-amazon-sale\u0026amp;event_label=Sonos%20Arc\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eSonos Arc\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. This smart soundbar came out in 2020 and received an \u003ca href=\"https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/sonos-arc\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"open in a new window\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u0026#34;excellent\u0026#34; review from PCMag\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e for its Dolby Atmos compatibility, ease of expansion, support for Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant, and its wide sound field and powerful bass (even without a subwoofer). Its current \u003cstrong\u003e$629 \u003c/strong\u003eprice is the cheapest it has ever been (although it\u0026#39;s shipped and sold by a third-party Amazon store).\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n                        \u003cdiv\u003e\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://lifehacker.com/imagery/authors/01HF2FBG3NFZ3WZWX5Q6M3PDM4/image.fill.size_150x150.v1704301325.png\" alt=\"Daniel Oropeza caricature \" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\n                                            \u003c/p\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                \u003cp\u003eDaniel Oropeza\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eStaff Writer\u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                            \u003cp\u003eDaniel is a Staff Writer for Lifehacker. He served in the U.S. Navy, where he reached the rank of Petty Officer 3rd Class as a Logistic Specialist and was awarded a Navy Community Service Medal a